OL,3,CManx Care chief executive to stand
OL,4,Cdown from role in the summer
OL,6,FThe Chief Executive of Manx Care has
OL,7,Fannounced she will step down from her
OL,8,Frole this summer, after leading the
OL,9,FIsland's health service since its
OL,10,Finception.
OL,12,FTeresa Cope joined the public service
OL,13,Fin the Isle of Man in December 2020,
OL,14,Ftasked with launching the service
OL,15,Fduring the height of the Covid-19
OL,16,Fpandemic.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
