CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778674273
OL,3,CManx Care chief executive to stand
OL,4,Cdown from role in the summer
OL,6,FIn a statement, Cope said although she
OL,7,Fis "immensely proud" of the last five
OL,8,Fyears, she feels it is time to "pass
OL,9,Fthe baton on to someone else", as the
OL,10,FGovernance review into the
OL,11,Forganisation continues.
OL,13,FShe said: "I have therefore announced
OL,14,Fmy intention to step down and will be
OL,15,Fmoving with my family on to pastures
OL,16,Fnew later this year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778674273
OL,3,CManx Care chief executive to stand
OL,4,Cdown from role in the summer
OL,6,F"For now, however, it remains very
OL,7,Fmuch business as usual, and I will
OL,8,Fcontinue to work with the Board and
OL,9,Fcolleagues across the organisation so
OL,10,Fas to ensure there is a seamless
OL,11,Fhandover before I depart in the summer.
OL,13,F"I would like to take this opportunity
OL,14,Fto thank all my colleagues over these
OL,15,Flast five years for their support in
OL,16,Fhelping push forward the quality of
OL,17,Fcare on the Island."
