OL,3,CManx Care chief executive to stand
OL,4,Cdown from role in the summer
OL,6,FManx Care officially formed in April
OL,7,F2021, following recommendations from
OL,8,FSir Jonathan Michael's 2019 review
OL,9,Finto the Island's healthcare system.
OL,11,FChair of the Manx Care Board,
OL,12,FProfessor Wendy Reid, added: "The
OL,13,Fformation of Manx Care from a standing
OL,14,Fstart was a huge ask, and undoubtedly
OL,15,Fthere has been progress across many
OL,16,Fareas of governance, transparency and
OL,17,Fmost importantly care on the Island."
OL,26,@tD@^OU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/6
