FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778674273
OL,3,CManx Care chief executive to stand
OL,4,Cdown from role in the summer
OL,6,FMinister for Health and Social Care,
OL,7,FClaire Christian MHK, acknowledged the
OL,8,Ftiming of the departure in relation to
OL,9,Fthe ongoing scrutiny of the health
OL,10,Fbody.
OL,12,FShe said: "The Governance Review has
OL,13,Fpointed to a range of areas in which
OL,14,Fthings are working well, but also
OL,15,Fareas where improvements can be made
OL,16,Fand Tynwald have asked for these areas
OL,17,Fto be reviewed and opportunities for
OL,18,Fany improvements to come back.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
