OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,395,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F394A1778674273
OL,3,CManx Care chief executive to stand
OL,4,Cdown from role in the summer
OL,6,F"Teresa's decision to move on to the
OL,7,Fnext chapter of her career will allow
OL,8,Fus an opportunity to conclude the
OL,9,Freview before we proceed to recruit
OL,10,Fand I look forward to working with the
OL,11,Fteam including Teresa and Wendy and
OL,12,Fthe Manx Care Board on establishing
OL,13,Finterim arrangements going forward."
OL,26,@uD@dO]
